---
import "../styles/care.scss";
---

<article class="main__block palliative-n-hospice">
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_1">
    <h2 class="palliative-n-hospice__title-h2">
      Palliative Care and Hospice Care
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_2">
    <h3 class="palliative-n-hospice__title-h3">
      People suffering from dire medical conditions require specialized care
      that combines medical, psychological, and social treatment.
    </h3>
  </div>
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_3">
    <div class="palliative-n-hospice__image-wrapper">
      <img
        src="/images/doctor-and-patient-1.png"
        alt="Doctor and patient"
        class="palliative-n-hospice__image"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_4">
    <p class="palliative-n-hospice__text">
      This includes diseases like cancer, ALS, Alzheimer&rsquo;s,
      Parkinson&rsquo;s, HIV, and more. These diseases can leave family members
      not knowing how to better the quality of their loved one&rsquo;s life.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_5">
    <h3 class="palliative-n-hospice__title-h3">
      We provide certified professionals who are educated in palliative and
      hospice care.
    </h3>
  </div>
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_6">
    <div class="palliative-n-hospice__image-wrapper">
      <img
        src="/images/doctor-and-patient-2.png"
        alt="Doctor and patient, too"
        class="palliative-n-hospice__image"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="palliative-n-hospice__item palliative-n-hospice__item_7">
    <p class="palliative-n-hospice__text">
      Our goal is to ensure that our patients have the best life they can while
      they go through this difficult time. This way, you do not have to worry
      about your family members spending their final days in a hospital. Now,
      your family members can live the rest of their lives comfortably in their
      own homes.
    </p>
  </div>
</article>
